        "last_activity_date": 1466338002,
        "creation_date": 1466338002,
        "body": "<blockquote>\n  <p>Is there any oops technique so that i can access this method from\n  other activity?<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>You can create a Utility class, and declare this method isOnline() as a static function over there (protected or public depending on your package design).<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>protected static boolean isOnline()\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>From any activity call it like this<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>boolean isPhoneOnline = Utility.isOnline();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Hope this helps.<\/p>\n",
